    <div class="padded-box space-sink-example-text-crop space-sink-example--m space-sink-example--line-height-2">
        Wrapping lines of text to illustrate <br>
        line height differences. Line height 2.
    </div>


    <p>Useful for ensuring only system padding & margins are creating space between and within elements. Also useful for vertically aligning elements&rsquo; top or bottom edges.</p>

